Installation:

  git clone https://github.com/whiss1/dotfiles.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

  ln -s ~/dotfiles/vimrc ~/.vimrc
  ln -s ~/dotfiles/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Git commands

  Copying files from Github:

    git clone "url of file you want" "position in directory"

  Copying submodules from Github (plugins):

    Need cd ~/.vim before executing
    git submodule add "url of folder in Github" ~/.vim/bundle/"plugin name"

  Functions to apply after making changes to files to upload to Github:

    git add .
    git commit -m "text explaining changes made"
    git push

  Updating setting on another machine from Github:

    git pull

  Updating submodules (plugins) on another machine:

    git submodule update --init

